SATOR AREPO TENET OPERA ROTAS<BR>
<BR>
AI MUR VIA U POS DES-DE<BR>
EW TU VIA VID EST MIS-VE<BR>
A AI SOL LEM VIA AN-QUAS<BR>
WIS ARK U DE VIA FEL-TAS<BR>
APTA VIA EST-RE ARK-TE<BR>
AK-SI MUR EST WI-DE DUK-TAS<BR>
<BR>
FAR TO THE SOUTH ON ISLAND THERE<BR>
AN ORDER OLD BOTH BOLD AND FAIR<BR>
ON ISLE OF DEEDS MUST YE NOW WAIT<BR>
TO FIND THE ONE TO SHARE THY FATE<BR>
A SILVER SERPENT WILL HE WEAR<BR>
HE MUST RETURN THROUGH SERPENT'S GATE<BR>
<BR>
IN SHAMEFUL PLACE A MAIDEN KIND<BR>
HER CAPTOR THERE YE MUST NOW FIND<BR>
WITH CUP OF WINE A CHALLENGE MADE<BR>
A DUEL TO DEATH IN SUNNY GLADE<BR>
THOUGH TRAP'S BEEN SET THY WORD MUST BIND<BR>
AND HONOR'S DEBT WILL THEN BE PAID<BR>
<BR>
KODEKS DE AN-RE-SKI-DE BEN-TAS<BR>
