KODEKS SEM-DE:<BR>
<BR>
ISTA EST QUO INIT VEST-TAS<BR>
LOK SON OM KLI-TEM AN FEL-TAS<BR>
SOL SI U FIN RIT BEN-FIN-DE<BR>
SA SKI-TAS U NES EST UUS-LE<BR>
FER LAP TRAK TER-ORT DE BEN-TAS<BR>
EW LEM BE-RE IN-LE OM-DE<BR>
<BR>
NEAR PEACEFUL RIVER WITHOUT FLAW<BR>
FAR FROM THE FENS WHERE RAVENS CAW<BR>
THE WORDS OF OLD ABOVE WILL BE<BR>
WRITTEN DOWN BELOW FOR THEE<BR>
THE SEVENTH TIME BY RULE OF LAW<BR>
NOW HEED THE WORDS OF WISDOM'S PLEA<BR>
