APTA VIA EST-RE ARK-TE<BR>
AK-SI MUR EST WI-DE DUK-TAS<BR>
<BR>
IN SPIRITWOOD FIND KROMZEK'S BANE<BR>
THE HOME HE LOST HE MUST REGAIN<BR>
IN LANDS OF OLD NO LONGER LOST<BR>
NOW JUNGLE LANDS THAT ONCE WERE FROST<BR>
AND SERPENT'S FROM THE PAST NOW REIGN<BR>
HIS AID TO SEEK AND WORTH THE COST<BR>
<BR>
WHERE VICTIMS BLOOD AN ALTER SMEAR<BR>
ABANDON HOPE WHO ENTER HERE<BR>
THE ENTRANCE TO ABYSMAL PITS<BR>
BENEATH THE STAIRS WHERE TEMPLE SITS<BR>
'NEATH STANDING STONES THE KEY IS NEAR<BR>
THE SIGN OF PEACE IS ALL THAT FITS<BR>
<BR>
KODEKS DE AN-RE-SKI-DE BEN-TAS<BR>
