EW LEM BE-RE IN-LE OM-DE<BR>
<BR>
WHERE LAVA RISES IN A POOL<BR>
NEAR MISTMOOR ISLE WHERE GARGOYLES RULE<BR>
THE WORDS OF OLD ABOVE WILL BE<BR>
WRITTEN DOWN BELOW FOR THEE<BR>
A FINAL TASK TO FIND THE JEWEL<BR>
NOW HEED THE WORDS OF WISDOM'S PLEA<BR>
