SOLUS SACERADOTIBUS:<BR>
SATOR AREPO TENET OPERA ROTAS<BR>
<BR>
AI MUR VIA U POS DES-DE<BR>
EW TU VIA VID EST MIS-VE<BR>
A AI SOL LEM VIA AN-QUAS<BR>
WIS ARK U DE VIA FEL-TAS<BR>
APTA VIA EST-RE ARK-TE<BR>
AK-SI MUR EST WI-DE DUK-TAS<BR>
<BR>
ON TO A LAND ONCE RULED BY PRIDE<BR>
NOW LAID IN RUINS WHERE ALL HAVE DIED<BR>
AMONGST THE FLOCKS AND SHEPARDS MEEK<BR>
A SIMPLE LASS PROTECTS THE WEAK<BR>
WITHOUT HER AID CLOSE BY THY SIDE<BR>
THOU SHALT NOT FIND THE BOOK YE SEEK<BR>
<BR>
WHEN ALL THE PEOPLE KNOW THY NAME<BR>
AND OFFER THEE BOTH WEALTH AND FAME<BR>
INSIDE OF PRIDE YE MUST NOW LOOK<BR>
AND READ THE WORDS FROM WISDOM'S BOOK<BR>
FOR HUBRIS NOW MAY LEAD TO SHAME<BR>
FROM WARRIOR'S SWORD FORGE SHEPARD'S CROOK<BR>
<BR>
KODEKS DE AN-RE-SKI-DE BEN-TAS<BR>
<BR>
SOL LEM AD OM-DE VEST-TAS TRAK BEN-TAS CAN-LE LEG KODEKS<BR>
<BR>
KODEKS UL:<BR>
<BR>
KNOW HONOR'S BANE IS HIDDEN STILL<BR>
AND GUARDED WELL BY FORCE OF WILL<BR>
IT DOTH NOT SLEEP IT DOTH NOT EAT<BR>
CANNAE BE HARMED BY COLD OR HEAT<BR>
WHAT DOTH NOT LIVE YE CANNAE KILL<BR>
BY WORDS ALONE YE MUST DEFEAT<BR>
<BR>
TO FREE THE LAND YE MUST NOW GO<BR>
AND WALK AMIDST THE STARS BELOW<BR>
FROM LANDS OF COLD TO LANDS OF FIRE<BR>
FROM RIVER'S BIRTH TO FUNERAL PYRE<BR>
ALONG A PATH FROM LONG AGO<BR>
WHERE ONCE THERE WAS A PEACFUL SHIRE<BR>
<BR>
ON PAST A SHRINE OF BLOOD ONCE CLEAN<BR>
AND TO A CAVE THAT'S SELDOM SEEN<BR>
A RIDDLE SOLVED WILL BE THE PRICE<BR>
TO FREE THE LAND THROUGH SACRIFICE<BR>
THE WORDS ARE ON A STAFF OF GREEN<BR>
ACROSS THE SEA TO ISLES OF ICE<BR>
<BR>
BEYOND THE GATE BENEATH THE FALLS<BR>
THEN GO YE THERE E'ER EVENING CALLS<BR>
THROUGH THE TUNNEL 'NEATH THE LAKE<BR>
THE SLEEPER THERE YE MUST NOT WAKE<BR>
UP TO A ROOM WITH ONLY WALLS<BR>
A DARKENED THORN HIS SOUL TO TAKE<BR>
<BR>
AND NOW THE WAY AHEAD IS BARRED<BR>
THE DOOR YE SEE IS BURNT AND CHARRED<BR>
CHIPPED AND BROKEN ON THE SEAMS<BR>
THOUGH NOTHING HERE IS AS IT SEEMS<BR>
THE KEY YE SEEK COMES FROM THE BARD<BR>
NEAR JUSTICE COURT THE ENTRANCE GLEAMS<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
KODEKS DE AN-RE-SKI-DE BEN-TAS<BR>
<BR>
SOL LEM AD OM-DE VEST-TAS TRAK BEN-TAS CAN-LE LEG KODEKS<BR>
<BR>
KODEKS FIN:<BR>
<BR>
WHERE POISON IS THE ONLY DOOR<BR>
THE CEILING REACHES TO THE FLOOR<BR>
UPON THE GROUND ARE STARS OF BLUE<BR>
E'ER DAY IS DONE YE MUST BE THROUGH<BR>
TO FIND OUR HOPE IN ANCIENT LORE<BR>
THE STARS MUST GLOW WITH SCARLET HUE<BR>
<BR>
WITHIN A CIRCLE AND A STAR<BR>
IT RESTS UPON A CRYSTAL BAR<BR>
LOCKED IN COLD WITH BLUISH GLOW<BR>
ONE WAY IS FIRE THE OTHER SNOW<BR>
THE PATH LIES NEAR THOUGH END IS FAR<BR>
THE FINAL PAGE THE WAY WILL SHOW<BR>
<BR>
ONCE ALL AROUND WILL GIVE THEE STRENGTH<BR>
TWICE ALL AROUND WILL MAKE THEE THINK<BR>
THRICE ALL AROUND WILL MAKE THEE BOLD<BR>
THOUGH THREE ALONE WON'T SEAL OR HOLD<BR>
BE WARY LEST YE BREAK THE LINK<BR>
AND FIRE IN THE STARS GROWS COLD<BR>
<BR>
THE STARS MUST SHINE BY LIGHT OF DAY<BR>
AND DANGER WAITS FOR THEE THAT STAY<BR>
FOR WITH THE NIGHT IT WILL AWAKE<BR>
THE WARDS WON'T HOLD THE BONDS WILL BREAK<BR>
AND EVER MORE A PRICE TO PAY<BR>
THE GROUND WILL SPLIT THE EARTH WILL SHAKE<BR>
<BR>
THE RISK IS HIGH FOR IF YE FAIL<BR>
THE LIGHT WILL DIM THE SUN WILL PALE<BR>
AND EVIL WILL AT LAST BE FREE<BR>
YE CANNAE STAY AND ALL MUST FLEE<BR>
AND FROM THE JUST WILL RISE A WAIL<BR>
AND LANDS WILL SINK BENEATH THE SEA<BR>
<BR>
KODEKS DE AN-RE-SKI-DE BEN-TAS<BR>
<BR>
SOL LEM AD OM-DE VEST-TAS TRAK BEN-TAS CAN-LE LEG KODEKS<BR>
<BR>
TO GAIN YE WISDOM FROM THE SCROLL<BR>
HIDDEN PATHS MUST BE THY GOAL<BR>
EACH VERSE THAT'S HERE MAY HOLD THE KEY<BR>
<BR>
WHEN READ WITH CARE THE WISE WILL SEE<BR>
IN EVERY TEST THERE IS A TOLL<BR>
SINCE VIRTUE EVER HATH A FEE<BR>
PATHWAYS LOST MUST BE REFOUND<BR>
SHOWN BY LIGHT WITH CRYSTAL SOUND<BR>
<BR>
KNOWLEDGE LOST WHEN WORLD WAS YOUNG<BR>
NOW IS FOUND IN STRANGEST TONGUE<BR>
ONLY WORDS THAT NOW CONFOUND<BR>
WILL HAVE EFFECT WHEN THEY ARE SUNG<BR>
<BR>
SOL SI SAENGKT-LE O AK-SI-MUR<BR>
OK TIM U EST NES-LE LOK JUR<BR>
LOK-LE ANTE SON DE AUD-CHAR<BR>
U-DE VEST-TAS EST A-VA-TAR<BR>
SA EST FIN-LE SOL O AN-MUR<BR>
<BR>
SI U IN-WIS LOK LING DE GAR<BR>
AI-RE MUR A-PER-TER EX-POR<BR>
CHAR DE VEST-TAS EST-LE WIS-LOR<BR>
EW U EST-RE NES-LE REKSI<BR>
RES TRAK KUAE RE TE-MANI<BR>
AMO DON-RE U VER EW KOR<BR>
DES-DE TER-ORT EST-RE ATRI<BR>
ORT SOL ARK-TE VIA ANTE<BR>
TER-POR TURN U NES LOR DES-DE<BR>
ITA AGRA BAL-LEM KU SON<BR>
BEH-DE AUD-CHAR NES-RE LEM DON<BR>
UN A-REP-O LOK NOM LEM-DE<BR>
SKI AN-KAL-RE ISTA DAEMON<BR>
