Hail and well met; and greetings from the Vigils of Norrath! Allow me to introduce myself; I am Finnigan, a Ranger of Karana now in my 44th season. I belong to a small guild of some fifteen or so individuals from Surefall Glade.

[OOC: We are a small, role-playing guild of mid-level characters (20's thru 40's)on Morell Thule Server]

I have been sent by my guild to seek your aid in a matter that may be of some interest to you. It is a rather complicated tale that will take some time in the telling, so please hear me out.

Several months past, I found myself alone in Surefall Glade with the exception of a young Bard named Tiliki.  This young Bard seemed quite upset and was very insistent, so I stopped to speak with her. She spoke to me in a language that I had never heard before, and at first I thought she must be a stranger to Norrath, 

